....Football Team Cards

<!-- Overview -->

This project is a simple web application that displays football team statistics and player information in a structured format. Users can filter players based on their positions and view key details about the team.

<!-- Features -->

Displays team statistics including team name, sport type, year, and head coach.

Provides a dropdown menu to filter players based on their positions.

Dynamically loads player cards for better user interaction.

<!-- Technologies Used -->

HTML: Structure of the webpage.

CSS: Styling through an external stylesheet (football-team.css).

JavaScript: Handles dynamic content and interactions via (football.js).

<!-- File Structure -->

index.html - The main HTML file containing the team statistics and dropdown for filtering players.

football-team.css - Stylesheet for designing the layout and structure.

football.js - JavaScript file for handling dynamic content like updating team stats and filtering player cards.

<!-- How to Use -->

Open index.html in a web browser.

Team statistics will be displayed dynamically.

Use the dropdown menu to filter players by their positions.

The player cards will update based on the selected filter.

<!-- Setup -->

Download or clone the repository.

Ensure all required files (index.html, football-team.css, and football.js) are in the same directory.

Open index.html in a browser.

<!-- Future Enhancements -->

Add player images to the player cards.

Improve UI with animations and enhanced styling.

Fetch real-time team data from an API.

